sequenceDiagram
    actor CLI/App
    participant EM as ExtensionManager
    participant FS as Filesystem
    participant Ext as Extension Instance
    participant Agent as Agent

    CLI/App->>EM: loadExtensions()
    EM->>FS: discover extension dirs
    FS-->>EM: list of extension paths
    EM->>EM: read manifests (extension.json)
    EM->>EM: build dependency graph
    EM->>EM: topological sort
    EM->>Ext: new Extension(context, manifest)
    Ext->>Ext: constructor
    EM->>Ext: init()
    Ext->>Ext: setup internal state, register event listeners
    EM->>Ext: enable()
    Ext->>Ext: provide.tools/prompts/etc
    Ext->>Agent: agent.setTools([...]) (or provide API)
    EM->>EM: repeat for next extension (in order)
    EM-->>CLI/App: all loaded